Sub: Extended Support to 2016 Graduated/Graduating Students


Dear Student,

The IC & SR, in its efforts to encourage and enable the spirit of
innovation within the IIT Madras Innovation Ecosystem,  has created a
provision to provide support to immediately graduating students.  This is
to encourage the student to complete, or bring to the next logical step,
any projects/innovation that he has undertaken during his tenure within IIT
Madras.  This support is limited to a period of 6 months.  The support is
at the level of a Project Associate.

Desirous Students are requested to apply by filling up the form:

https://goo.gl/forms/XdRswIm1r99eYnGv2

The last date for applying for this is 31st Aug 2016.

Please make the best use of this opportunity. For additional information,
please feel free to contact either Prof. Mahesh Panchagnula (mvp@iitm.ac.in)
or Prof. Ashwin Mahalingam (mash@iitm.ac.in).



Vijay Dhavala



